Sample Database and Collection Creation

Commands for database creation
•	Create Database: use 
> use Employee
It is automatically switched to database Employee

•	To check your currently selected database: db
>db

•	Check database list: show dbs
>show dbs
admin  0.000GB
local  0.000GB

The Employee database is not present in list. To display database, you need to insert at least one document into it.
